org.block.project.block

Interface Block.AttachableBlock

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Block
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Block.AttachableBlock.StatementBlock
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAttachable, AbstractNumberOperation, MethodBlock, SumOperation, VariableBlock
    Enclosing interface:
    Block

    public static interface Block.AttachableBlock
extends Block
    If the Block requires additional information to function properly that is in code form, then it should implement Attachable. This allows users to add blocks directly to this block
